Forger
A Forger is a specialist in creating false documents, credentials, identity
papers, and counterfeit goods. In the Rifts world where border controls and
faction IDs are matters of life and death, a skilled Forger is invaluable.

Forgers choose from Rogue, Technical, and Physical skill categories. They are
not fighters but their social and technical skills make them essential members
of any team operating across faction lines.

Attribute requirements: IQ 11, PP 10.
Starting equipment: Forgery tools and inks, portable scanner and printer,
blank credential stock, one concealed sidearm, and a set of false identity
documents of their own creation.
